    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK466">
<l>ceytakka alla ceyakkeṭum ceytakka</l>
<l>ceyyāmai yāṉuṅ keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will perish who does not what is not fit to do and he also will perish who does not do what it is fit to do.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
